rn the buildings.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh  avaulted roofing, enclosed courtyards, architectural design, architecture, building, construction, egypt, tradition, nubia, native, indigenous, mud bricks, luxor, new gourna, village, hassan fathy, poverty, rural, community, neighborhood, adornment, decoration, mudwork, lattice, claustra, crafts, revival, folk art, nonfiction, vaulting, masons, masonry, climate, kinship, labor, materials.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Press eBook Package Archive 1960-1989z978311066784440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226239149423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226239149/original  a978-3-11-066784-4  University of Chicago Press eBook Package Archive 1960-1989c1960d1989  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles